snippet.title: Oriental Magnetic Yellow (OMY) - Beyond the Muscle [1995]
snippet.description:
See also:
Good Pierrot - http://youtu.be/D4XcZyB8Dq0

A parody band of Yellow Magic Orchestra, formed by VGM composers. The members were: Shinji Hosoe, Nobuyoshi Sano, Takayuki Aihara and Hiroto Sasaki.
